OL,3,CCalls for Guernsey to introduce a
OL,4,Cpublic sex offenders register
OL,6,FPressure has been put on Guernsey
OL,7,Fpoliticians to introduce a public sex
OL,8,Foffenders register on the island.
OL,10,FA letter has been sent to all deputies
OL,11,Farguing that a fully public register
OL,12,Fwould help protect the community.
OL,14,FThis would take it beyond legislation
OL,15,Fin both Jersey and the UK, where
OL,16,Fparents, carers and teachers can
OL,17,Fformally ask the police if they have
OL,18,Fsuspicions about someone.
