OL,3,CCalls for Guernsey to introduce a
OL,4,Cpublic sex offenders register
OL,6,FJane, whose name has also been
OL,7,Fchanged, was assaulted when she was a
OL,8,Fchild.
OL,10,FShe says: "Places where he has worked,
OL,11,Fwhere I don't think he should be
OL,12,Fworking. I approached his boss and
OL,13,Fexplained the situation... I don't
OL,14,Fthink he was in that job much longer."
OL,16,FSarah's Law, in memory of murdered
OL,17,Fschool girl Sarah Payne, already
OL,18,Fallows parents, carers and guardians
OL,19,Fto find out about suspected child sex
OL,20,Fabusers in the UK and Jersey.
