OL,6,FA fully public register is very rare,
OL,7,Fand while Guernsey does not have
OL,8,FSarah's Law, if a risk has been
OL,9,Fidentified, the police will sometimes
OL,10,Fgive information to third parties.
OL,12,FITV Channel News has approached Home
OL,13,FAffairs for comment.
